      <h2>Research Findings & Analysis</h2>
      <p>The combined JSON database has proven invaluable for analyzing different culinary trends and patterns across Mississippi's community cookbook history. Here are some of the key findings that Suwan and I have analyzed and discovered:</p>

      <!-- Collapsible Essay Section -->
      <div class="essay-collapsible">
